---
// "Who I am" section.
---
<section class="about-section" id="about">
  <div class="about-card">

    <!-- Photo LEFT -->
    <div class="about-img-wrap">
      <img src="/New Profile.jpg" alt="Eliya Kapach" />
    </div>

    <!-- Text RIGHT -->
    <div class="about-text">
      <h3 class="about-heading">Behind the Lens</h3>
      <p class="about-intro">I'm Eliya — filmmaker, content creator, and visual storyteller.</p>
      <p>I work with brands that want more than good-looking content —<br/>They want something that makes people feel and respond.</p>
      <p>
        My work is rooted in real experiences: travel, speed, silence, movement.
        I translate those into stories that carry emotion, depth, and presence.
        Every project is led by me, end-to-end, with full creative control.
      </p>
      <p class="highlight">The result?<br/>Films that don't just look impressive — they stay with people.</p>

      <div class="skills-wrap">
        <p class="skills-label">What I do</p>
        <div class="skills-tags">
          <span class="skill-tag">Direction</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Cinematography</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Color Grading</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Editing</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Storytelling</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Sound Design</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
